snippet.title: Just Read The Instructions - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://buff.ly/421FouS 
Beta signup: https://buff.ly/41NOqf0
Discord: https://discord.gg/z3w7TUaQ

Fight off thousands of enemies with a variety of powerful weapons in this surreal co-op shooter. Enter a simulation controlled by a corrupted AI to disrupt and destroy it. Explore procedural worlds, eliminate enemies, break logic, and watch it collapse.

It's an indie game solo developed by me, Tobias, and I hope you like it!

Knackelibang on social media
